	<AlienRace.ThingDef_AlienRace ParentName="FRealms_HumanoidRaceBase">
		<defName>FRealms_Halfling</defName>
		<label>Halfling</label>
		<description>Also known as Hin, or the "quick folk" amongst themselves, Halflings are small humanoid creatures, very similar in appearance to Humans, but around half their size.</description>
